resources.string: Ilungisa ngamandla isibonisi esisuselwa kumaleveli aseduze okukhanya
Nge-Pixel Imprint, ungavula ifoni yakho usebenzisa izigxivizo zeminwe yakho. Ngokuphepha, le nketho idinga ukukhiya kwesikrini okuyisipele.
Khetha ukukhiya isikrini kwesipele ukuze usebenzise nge-Pixel Imprint
Ngokungeziwe ekuvuleni ifoni yakho, ungaphinda usebenzise i-Pixel Imprint ukuze ugunyaze ukuthenga nokufinyelela kohlelo lokusebenza. Funda kabanzi

"Sebenzisa izigxivizo zominwe zakho ukuvula ifoni yakho noma uvume ukuthenga.
Inothi: Isigxivizo sakho somunwe singaphepha kancane kunephethini eqinile nomai-PIN."

"Nge-Pixel Imprint, ungasebenzisa izigxivizo zeminwe zakho ukuze ugunyaze ukuthenga noma ungene ngemvume kuzinhlelo zokusebenza.
Qaphela ukuthi ungeza izigxivizo zeminwe zikabani. Noma iziphi izigxivizo zeminwe ezingeziwe zizokwazi ukwenza lezi zinto.
Yazi: Awukwazi ukusebenzisa izigxivizo zeminwe zakho ukuze uvule le divayisi. Ukuze uthole olunye ulwazi, xhumana nomqondisi wenhlangano yakho."
Vele uthinte inzwa ye-Pixel Imprint ukuze uvuse uphinde uvule ifoni yakho.
